Package: euissR
Type: Package
Title: EUISS Visual Identity for Ggplot2
Version: 0.2.0
Author: cd_trich
Maintainer: <christian.g.dietrich@gmail.com>
Description: Custom ggplot2 theme, geoms and color palettes for the EU Institute 
    for Security Studies visual identity. Features a dual-mode system: draft mode 
    for preview/sharing (PNG, SVG with PT Sans fonts) and print mode for Adobe 
    Illustrator post-production (PDF with reliable font embedding). Includes 
    color palettes, utility functions, and streamlined export workflows.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    needs,
    png
Config/testthat/edition: 3
